edian). To allow better monitoring and optimizing sampling effort at the border, we recommend that border protection agencies report all the data (the number of infested units found together with the sample size of the inspection) instead of only that the consignment failed inspection.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Trouv\u00e9, Rapha\u00ebl", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Robinson, Andrew P.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 5", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bc9bbf51db80eb9b9f95ca567cd3aabd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/8382b9ed472a24849bc0ddf925bc2f8b822dd3102096a14bdeb6fa417ab18051", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/D7ENFLQM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/D7ENFLQM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/db85dd8d245a2aa8536b1b4d5e4ba473!/b122141-124297", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/risa.13592", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "6", "pages": "992-1003", "title": "Risk Analysis", "volume": "41"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bc9bbf51db80eb9b9f95ca567cd3aabd"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:g